Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.88,0:22:02.07,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,在你的(我的)脑海里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.74,0:22:05.94,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,歌剧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.93,0:22:13.54,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是 歌剧魅影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.42,0:22:22.36,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,在你所有的幻想中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.39,0:22:25.96,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,你一直清楚的明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.18,0:22:29.46,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人与那个神秘的迷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.67,0:22:33.21,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,其实就是你
