Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.70,0:23:20.65,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,我的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.39,0:23:36.48,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,歌唱 歌唱 歌唱吧 我的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.85,0:25:18.70,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,一位女士用小提琴
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.27,0:25:22.39,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,向水手们弹奏着
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.92,0:25:39.27,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,倾听着那蛊惑之音
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.04,0:25:56.58,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁把我的手绑在舵盘上了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.80,0:26:03.86,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉天昏地暗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.90,0:26:06.63,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,“来我这里吧”
