Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.01,0:41:58.47,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,“我生于紫色悬瀑中”
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.11,0:42:00.67,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,“身体虚弱”
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.75,0:42:02.69,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,“但并没有受到诅咒”
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.82,0:42:05.40,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,“我对这个世界没任何感觉”
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.23,0:42:07.53,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,“只为这段旅程而活着”
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.99,0:42:12.24,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,“一天晚上 我梦到”
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.22,0:42:15.27,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,“一朵正在枯萎的白玫瑰”
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.35,0:42:17.52,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,“一个婴儿”
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.28,0:42:20.07,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,“一生都沉浸在孤独中”
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.54,0:42:23.94,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,“我梦到了我的未来”
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.03,0:42:25.49,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,“回想起我的过去”
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.52,0:42:28.40,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,“亲眼目睹了”
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.62,0:42:29.62,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,“野兽的美丽”
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.99,0:43:06.29,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,那些感觉都去向了何处
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.81,0:43:14.70,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么所有的笑声都停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.60,0:43:19.66,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我在死去后
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.62,0:43:23.91,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,才能得到爱
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.48,0:43:31.10,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,赶快回来保佑这孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.18,0:43:53.36,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,我如何才能再有曾经的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.04,0:44:01.70,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,再给我次机会 我会回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.83,0:44:06.88,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我在死去后
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.77,0:44:11.11,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,才能得到爱
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.65,0:44:18.17,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,赶快回来保佑孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.59,0:44:22.50,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,多想想我
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.81,0:44:24.64,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,足以生成回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.48,0:44:31.24,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,再一次来保佑孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.71,0:44:48.20,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,一生中我从未感到过如此孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.14,0:44:51.29,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,就如同我喝水时
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.32,0:44:54.42,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,杯子在计量着我的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.44,0:44:57.55,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,一滴毒液
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.60,0:45:00.56,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,落在了人类的杯子里
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.59,0:45:03.56,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,喝下它
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.59,0:45:10.40,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,意味着走左手边的路
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.78,0:45:44.28,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我在死去后
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.79,0:45:47.27,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,才能得到爱
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.82,0:45:55.55,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,赶快回来保佑孩子
