Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.09,0:46:26.18,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,再一次来保佑孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.23,0:46:46.71,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,“那些感觉都去向了何处”
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.83,0:46:49.39,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,“为什么我爱你那样的爱”
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.60,0:46:51.42,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,“会是最重的罪恶”
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.36,0:46:54.64,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,“现在 被诅咒着 被思念所缠绕着”
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.97,0:46:57.11,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,“不久将了无牵挂”
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.72,0:46:59.04,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,“不再遭受这人间的痛苦”
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.35,0:47:03.28,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,“我的故事便是那最悲惨的事实”
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.61,0:47:06.27,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,“时间将会为我们偿还”
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.30,0:47:07.69,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,“但是 却只有泥沙和尘土”
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.73,0:47:10.01,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,“以及黑暗的、寂静的坟墓”
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.35,0:47:13.65,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,“记住 我的孩子”
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.69,0:47:15.32,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,“若不清白”
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.36,0:47:17.65,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,“那十字架只是块铁”
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.05,0:47:20.87,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,“希望只是幻影”
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.20,0:47:22.75,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,“所谓海洋的灵魂”
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.09,0:47:25.32,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,“仅仅只是个名字”
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.89,0:47:28.96,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,“那孩子将保佑你”
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.06,0:47:31.29,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,“守护你 到永远”
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.89,0:47:58.21,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,大师
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.25,0:47:59.58,zhongwengeci,,0000,0000,0000,,学徒
